0161i trgovini."],"Sale status":["Stanje razprodaje"],"Show only products on sale":["Poka\u017ei samo izdelke iz razprodaje"],"An error has prevented the block from being updated.":["Napaka je prepre\u010dila posodobitev bloka."],"%d term":["%d izraz","%d izraza","%d izrazi","%d izrazov"],"%1$s, has %2$d term":["%1$s, ima %2$d izraz","%1$s, ima %2$d izraza","%1$s, ima %2$d izraze","%1$s, ima %2$d izrazov"],"%1$s, has %2$d product":["%1$s, ima %2$d izdelek","%1$s, ima %2$d izdelka","%1$s, ima %2$d izdelke","%1$s, ima %2$d izdelkov"],"We are currently working on improving our cart and checkout blocks to provide merchants with the tools and customization options they need.":["Prizadevamo si izbolj\u0161ati razdelke ko\u0161aric in zaklju\u010dka nakupa, da trgovcem zagotovimo orodja in mo\u017enosti prilagajanja, ki jih potrebujejo."],"Loading\u2026":["Nalaganje \u2026"],"Feedback?":["Odziv?"],"Give us your feedback.":["Oddajte nam va\u0161 odziv."],"Advanced Filters":["Napredni filtri"],"Product Summary":["Povzetek izdelka"],"Display the title of a product.":["Poka\u017eite naslov izdelka."],"Display a short description about a product.":["Poka\u017eite kratek opis izdelka."],"The following error was returned":["Vrnjena je bila naslednja napaka"],"The following error was returned from the API":["API je vrnil naslednjo napako"],"No results for %s":["Ni rezultatov za %s"],"Search results updated.":["Rezultati iskanja so posodobljeni."],"Clear all":["Po\u010disti vse"],"Remove %s":["Odstrani %s"],"%d item selected":["Izbran %d predmet","Izbrana %d predmeta","Izbrani %d predmeti","Izbranih %d predmetov"],"Search for items":["Poi\u0161\u010dite predmete"],"No items found.":["Ni najdenih predmetov."],"Clear all selected items":["Po\u010disti vse izbrane predmete"],"Product attribute search results updated.":["Rezultati iskanja po atributih izdelkov so posodobljeni."],"Pick at least two attributes to use this setting.":["Za uporabo te nastavitve izberite vsaj dva atributa."]